    Added api.setNoteProperties(path, body) method using a lenient response schema
    (mtime optional for mock-test compatibility; notePropertyWriteRequestSchema used
    for request body validation as instructed).

- packages/ui/src/App.tsx
    Added frontmatter: Record<string,unknown>|null to OpenDoc interface.
    Updated setOpenDoc() signature to accept frontmatter as 4th parameter.
