    (null for new-note creation which has no frontmatter in putNote response).
    Imported BookmarkStar; rendered it in editor-header after save-status when
    route.kind==='note' && doc!==null && preview===null, keyed by doc.path so it
    remounts on note change.

- packages/ui/src/components/BookmarkStar.tsx  [NEW]
    Functional component. Props: docPath, initialFrontmatter.
    State: bookmarked (bool, init from initialFrontmatter.bookmark), mode (null=loading).
    On mount: api.getHealth() → setMode; error defaults to 'full'.
    Click handler: blocked when mode!==null&&mode!=='full'; optimistic flip → API call →
    success: set from res.frontmatter.bookmark; failure: rollback.
    Renders button[data-testid=bookmark-star][data-bookmarked][aria-disabled].

- packages/ui/src/icons.tsx
    Added StarOutlineIcon (stroke only) and StarFilledIcon (fill+stroke).

- packages/ui/src/styles.css
    Added .bookmark-star rules: muted color, accent on hover, accent when .is-bookmarked,
    disabled opacity/cursor via [aria-disabled="true"].

